    <summary>Windows terminal multiplexer built for AI coding agents</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
## wmux — Windows Terminal Multiplexer for AI Agents

Split panes, manage sessions, and run Claude Code / Codex / Gemini CLI side by side.
Built-in MCP server lets AI agents control terminals programmatically.

### Features
- Tmux-style keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+B prefix)
- Spatial pane navigation
- Daemon mode with session persistence
- MCP server for AI agent integration
- System tray support
    ]]></description>
